### =========================================================
### User Auth API - SignUp / Login Scenario Collection
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

@email = qa.user1@attestry.io
@password = Password123!
@phone = 010-1234-5678

@adminEmail = platform.admin@attestry.local
@adminPassword = PlatformAdm1n!2026


@tenantId = fae5ddb4-e430-4e70-b8ae-841a0f80f9ec
@groupId = abb30794-beba-4b26-b4f1-4cc53323402a
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN


### 1) SignUp
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}


### 2) Login - admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}",
  "tenantId": null,
  "groupId": null
}




### 2) Login - Case A: tenantId/groupId 모두 null (membership 자동 선택 or owner-only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "tenantId": null,
  "groupId": null
}


### 3) Login - Case B: tenantId/groupId 모두 지정 (특정 membership 직접 선택)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}"
}


### 4) Login - Case C: tenantId만 지정, groupId는 null
### 현재 정책상 requested membership 매칭 없이 활성 membership fallback 선택
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "groupId": null
}


### 5) Login - Case D: tenantId는 null, groupId만 지정
### 현재 정책상 requested membership 매칭 없이 활성 membership fallback 선택
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "tenantId": null,
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}"
}


### 6) Login - Case E: tenantId/groupId 불일치 또는 비활성 membership (실패 기대)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "tenantId": "wrong-tenant-id",
  "groupId": "wrong-group-id"
}


### 7) Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 8) Verify Phone
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-phone
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
